"""make sure expected failure for too much data requested"""
requested_limit = self.max_limit + 10
data = coins.get_ohlc_cc(self.coin, requested_limit)
if data.shape[0] > self.max_limit:
    pytest.xfail('Max limit unexpected.  Expected={} Requested={} Returned={}'
        .format(self.max_limit, requested_limit, data.shape[0]))
